# 🗓️ Work Calendar App

A custom calendar app built with Django for managing work schedules, including fixed weekday shifts and rotating weekend teams.

## 🔧 Features

- Fixed weekday staff scheduling (Monday–Thursday)
- Rotating weekend teams (A, B, C, D) for Friday–Sunday
- Morning and evening shift support
- Admin panel for managing users and shifts
- Django-based backend with REST API (in progress)

## 🚀 Getting Started

### 1. Clone the Repository

```bash
git clone <your-repo-url>
cd <your-project-folder>


python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate  # On Windows: venv\Scripts\activate


pip install -r requirements.txt


python manage.py makemigrations
python manage.py migrate


python manage.py createsuperuser

python manage.py runserver
